{"tid":477270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世柒] 何志平 何以斷正喺美國手上","createTime":"2017-11-23T01:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:36:57.000Z","uid":56015,"like":128,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"701d203e38edf094eaf958002d3ec0bf0118e063","tid":477270,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"何志平 洗黑錢同行賄案，我終於有時間睇晒成份FBI Speical Agent寫嘅Sealed Complaint(可以話係起訴書，或公訴書)， 何志平 呢次斷正，可以咁講，你中國要搞非洲前，你班友都係搞掂香港嘅匯款系統先，仲話搞乜嘢人民幣離岸中心，班非洲佬一早堅持收美金，你搞好香港匯款系統好過。<br />\n<br />\n何志平 斷正喺美國嘅中轉銀行度<br />\n<br />\n大家要對國際匯款有基本概念先，除咗 SEPA 系統成員嘅歐元匯款外(果啲全部係歐洲央行結數，所以 SEPA 嘅轉帳係當本國轉帳論)，啲銀行係唔可能同全世界所有銀行對數，所以一定有中轉銀行(Intermediary Bank)，喺第三國代表另一方交易，而美金交易，幾乎一定喺晒紐約啲Intermediary Bank進行，一如人民幣交易，大部分 Intermediary Bank都係中國銀行一樣。而烏干達、乍得啲大人物，全部都係狼山原則之下嘅PEP，佢地係一早被人監視住。<br />\n<br />\n而最大鑊係，好多中東、非洲銀行啲中轉銀行，都係狼山集團(The Wolfsberg Group)成員，例如花旗銀行、HSBC、美國銀行、德意志銀行、渣打銀行，依家美國睇洗黑錢睇得咁緊，HSBC同德意志銀行被人罰錢罰到腳都軟，佢地發現可疑交易仲唔篤你灰就奇，因為舉報咗就自己甩身，但手續費照袋。所以 何志平 咁經香港匯錢法，唔死係好難嘅。<br />\n<br />\n所以起訴書有講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBank records reflect that on or about July 3, 2015, the Energy NGO/company wired $200,000 from a bank account in Hong Kong, through a bank in New York, to an account in the name of the Gadio Firm at a bank in Dubai. <br />\n<br />\n依家金管局有責任解畫，點解有筆黑錢可以喺香港經美國匯到，同埋何志平相關人士嘅往來銀行係邊一間，我唔信HSBC咁沙膽，我亦唔多信係Bank of China，因為太揚，況且Bank of China有自己嘅分行網絡，好多時啲Intermediary Bank都係自己啲分行，唔知香港邊間華資銀行最興做啲黑暗嘢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/16635/%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3%E5%96%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F16635%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2596%25BA%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B8%258A&d=zs9%2FH5MOh%2By9Cb8WNyr33QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=622b7855\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/16635/%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3%E5%96%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nSealed Complaint 原文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/usao-sdny/press-release/file/1012511/download\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpress-release%2Ffile%2F1012511%2Fdownload&d=zs9%2FH5MOh%2By9Cb8WNyr33QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8f7c2cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/usao-sdny/press-release/file/1012511/download</a>"},{"pid":"1cf2d905b722fdf718e89f39d90e4738b2ef65fc","tid":477270,"uid":91633,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"對住D用完即棄既CONDOM 有時候我真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fe95f00cd51579a996182823f88b5b533be4e1","tid":477270,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1ddab3baeefeb3b817e1c0d727ef36ae14a293","tid":477270,"uid":56015,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n份Sealed Complaint 好長, 54頁, 睇死人, 半分鐘睇一頁都要睇接近半粒鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac98d0dcbce70dce4e373f11a11369edb4b79c7","tid":477270,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"深入少少就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eec3030d734111145a3031de0869a1040ca79c7","tid":477270,"uid":19725,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深入少少就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 